OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FValentine's Day strike     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Takeaway delivery drivers are planning 
OL,6, to strike on Valentine's Day to demand 
OL,7, better pay and improved working        
OL,8, conditions.                            
OL,10,FThe action, impacting four food apps   
OL,11,Fincluding Deliveroo and Uber Eats, is  
OL,12,Fthought to involve as many as 3,000    
OL,13,Fdrivers and riders on Wednesday between
OL,14,F17:00 and 22:00 GMT.                   
OL,16,FOne cyclist taking part told the BBC   
OL,17,Ftheir pay was "absolutely ridiculous". 
OL,19,FDeliveroo said its riders "always earn 
OL,20,Fat least the national living wage".    
